==Russian==

===Indefinite pronoun===
'''кто-нибудь''' (któ-nibud’)
:'''N.B.''' &mdash; the particle [[-нибудь]] imparts a sense of indefiniteness similar to English [[any]]. The forms of '''кто-нибудь''' are usually associated with questions and negatives (like [[anybody]]), while [[кто-то]] is associated with affirmatives (like [[somebody]]).

# [[anybody]], [[anyone]], [[someone]] or other
#:*{{RUchar|Кто́-нибудь [[здесь]] [[быть|был]]?}} — ''Has anyone been here?''
#:*{{RUchar|[[кто-то|Кто́-то]] [[здесь]] [[быть|был]]!}} — ''Someone has been here!''

